      "do": [
        "建议：Pair every hero with the violet-sky atmospheric backdrop and a half-bleed portrait subject when possible。",
        "建议：Render display tiers at sub-default weights (460 / 540) — the warmth is the typographic signature。",
        "建议：Use rounded-rectangle CTAs at 8px radius everywhere except the hero (where pill-shaped is the rule)。",
