        "建议：Use warm dark grey {colors.ink} for body text — never pure black。"
      ],
      "dont": [
        "避免：use pill-shaped buttons in the body of the page; the pill is hero-only。",
        "避免：bump display weight above 540 unless using {body-strong} (700) for emphasized inline body。",
        "避免：render body text in pure black — the warm grey {#292827} is part of the brand。",
        "避免：omit the closing teal band — every marketing page closes with it。",
        "避免：introduce additional accent colors beyond indigo, violet-soft, teal, and the off-warm-greys。"
      ]
